title: Immaculate Unit. Detached Garage, Close to Lakes, Endless Amenities
posting_body: ['2Br/1Ba Apartment', 'Minnetonka Blvd, St Louis Park, MN', '$1860 per month', '2 bed, 1 bath', '1050 sq.', 'ft.', 'Dogs OK', 'Cats (declawed) OK', 'Deposit $500', 'DESCRIPTION', "This quiet beauty of St. Louis Park's hills and woods set the stage for your lifestyle.", "Stroll through the surrounding parkland - you'll have to keep reminding yourself that you're just minutes away from major Twin Cities highways, lakes, parks, shopping centers and downtown Minneapolis.", 'It is possible to live in a setting that is quiet and serene, yet allowing full participation in a dynamic metropolitan lifestyle.', "The interiors of your residence offer you space and a style you'll be proud of.", 'You may choose from four floorplan styles ranging from large one bedroom apartments to 1,500 square foot townhomes with three bedrooms and two and a half baths!', "The list of amenities and advantages is endless, and adds up to a lifestyle that's very distinguished.", ' Prices and availability are subject to change.', ' Photos may not represent exact unit.', 'Call Mike to tour.', 'show contact info', 'RENTAL FEATURES', 'Living room', 'Dining room', 'Walk-in closet', 'Range / Oven', 'Refrigerator', 'Dishwasher', 'Microwave', 'Balcony, Deck, or Patio', 'Air conditioning', 'Cable-ready', 'High-speed internet', 'Tile floor', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES', 'Clubhouse', 'Business center', 'Guest parking', 'Covered parking', 'Garage - Detached', 'LEASE TERMS', '12 months', 'Contact info:', 'Mike Miller', 'The Apartment Resource', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
